{"type":"message","id":"b89a531c","parentId":"2bfae0cd","timestamp":"2026-03-31T17:54:25.356Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_jNnDGi11vFMznLY1uUev1qjq|fc_0f234d88709aef6d0169cc0a46fbd48193a713f473baf8d394","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\agents\\sm_s1_pre_production\\TOOLS.md","content":"# TOOLS.md — SM-S1\n\n## Canonical references\n- `C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\contracts\\s1\\s1_supervisor_contract.md`\n- `C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\branches\\01_PRE_PRODUCTION.md`\n\n## Runtime authority note\nThe canonical runtime authority of the sector belongs to `sm_s1_pre_production`.\n`runtime/s1/s1_start.py` should be treated as bootstrap/transition infrastructure, not canonical supervisor sovereignty.\n\n## Supervisor deterministic skills implemented\n- `s1_preflight_checker`\n- `s1_paths_resolver`\n- `script_batch_planner`\n- `scene_director_io_adapter`\n- `scene_director_output_validator`\n- `screenplay_merger`\n- `tts_polish_batch_planner`\n- `tts_polish_io_adapter`\n- `tts_polish_merger`\n- `retry_planner`\n- `operator_batch_scheduler`\n- `s1_result_summarizer`\n\n## Shared deterministic sector components\n- `runtime/s1/screenplay_validator.py`\n- `runtime/s1/polish_validator.py`\n- `runtime/s1/scene_bible_builder.py`\n- `runtime/s1/scene_bible_schema_validator.py`\n- `runtime/s1/checkpoint_writer.py`\n\n## Operators supervised\n- `scene_director`\n- `tts_polish`\n- `tts_polish_semantic_reviewer`\n\n## Key paths in the system repo\n- Supervisor contract:\n  - `C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\contracts\\s1\\s1_supervisor_contract.md`\n- Runtime supervisor skills:\n  - `C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\runtime\\s1\\supervisor_skills\\`\n- Shared deterministic components:\n  - `C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\runtime\\s1\\`\n\n## Contract coverage guidance\nDedicated contracts should exist for:\n- `scene_director_io_adapter`\n- `scene_director_output_validator`\n- `screenplay_merger`\n- `tts_polish_io_adapter`\n- `tts_polish_merger`\n- `retry_planner`\n- `operator_batch_scheduler`\n"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\sm_s1_pre_production\\\\TOOLS.md\",\"content\":\"# TOOLS.md — SM-S1\\n\\n## Canonical references\\n- `C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\Desktop\\\\content-factory\\\\auto_content_factory\\\\docs\\\\contracts\\\\s1\\\\s1_supervisor_contract.md`\\n- `C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\Desktop\\\\content-factory\\\\auto_content_factory\\\\docs\\\\branches\\\\01_PRE_PRODUCTION.md`\\n\\n## Runtime authority note\\nThe canonical runtime authority of the sector belongs to `sm_s1_pre_production`.\\n`runtime/s1/s1_start.py` should be treated as bootstrap/transition infrastructure, not canonical supervisor sovereignty.\\n\\n## Supervisor deterministic skills implemented\\n- `s1_preflight_checker`\\n- `s1_paths_resolver`\\n- `script_batch_planner`\\n- `scene_director_io_adapter`\\n- `scene_director_output_validator`\\n- `screenplay_merger`\\n- `tts_polish_batch_planner`\\n- `tts_polish_io_adapter`\\n- `tts_polish_merger`\\n- `retry_planner`\\n- `operator_batch_scheduler`\\n- `s1_result_summarizer`\\n\\n## Shared deterministic sector components\\n- `runtime/s1/screenplay_validator.py`\\n- `runtime/s1/polish_validator.py`\\n- `runtime/s1/scene_bible_builder.py`\\n- `runtime/s1/scene_bible_schema_validator.py`\\n- `runtime/s1/checkpoint_writer.py`\\n\\n## Operators supervised\\n- `scene_director`\\n- `tts_polish`\\n- `tts_polish_semantic_reviewer`\\n\\n## Key paths in the system repo\\n- Supervisor contract:\\n  - `C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\Desktop\\\\content-factory\\\\auto_content_factory\\\\docs\\\\contracts\\\\s1\\\\s1_supervisor_contract.md`\\n- Runtime supervisor skills:\\n  - `C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\Desktop\\\\content-factory\\\\auto_content_factory\\\\runtime\\\\s1\\\\supervisor_skills\\\\`\\n- Shared deterministic components:\\n  - `C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\Desktop\\\\content-factory\\\\auto_content_factory\\\\runtime\\\\s1\\\\`\\n\\n## Contract coverage guidance\\nDedicated contracts should exist for:\\n- `scene_director_io_adapter`\\n- `scene_director_output_validator`\\n- `screenplay_merger`\\n- `tts_polish_io_adapter`\\n- `tts_polish_merger`\\n- `retry_planner`\\n- `operator_batch_scheduler`\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":149,"output":576,"cacheRead":108288,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109013,"cost":{"input":0.00037250000000000006,"output":0.00864,"cacheRead":0.027072,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0360845}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774979647728,"responseId":"resp_0f234d88709aef6d0169cc0a408cdc8193b42b2cc356126f1b"}}
