{"type":"message","id":"2ef9de81","parentId":"6cee3f02","timestamp":"2026-03-31T18:31:32.724Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_l5Wzv67EG6pkjYv4Tjsyzi7T|fc_0f234d88709aef6d0169cc1300a81c8193af8f324fa61e5ca1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\agents\\sm_s1_pre_production\\TOOLS.md","oldText":"## Contract coverage guidance\nDedicated contracts should exist for:\n- `scene_director_io_adapter`\n- `scene_director_output_validator`\n- `screenplay_merger`\n- `tts_polish_io_adapter`\n- `tts_polish_merger`\n- `retry_planner`\n- `operator_batch_scheduler`\n","newText":"## Contract coverage guidance\nDedicated contracts should exist for:\n- `scene_director_io_adapter`\n- `scene_director_output_validator`\n- `screenplay_merger`\n- `tts_polish_io_adapter`\n- `tts_polish_merger`\n- `retry_planner`\n- `operator_batch_scheduler`\n\nDedicated shared deterministic contracts should exist for:\n- `screenplay_validator`\n- `polish_validator`\n- `scene_bible_builder`\n- `scene_bible_schema_validator`\n"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\sm_s1_pre_production\\\\TOOLS.md\",\"oldText\":\"## Contract coverage guidance\\nDedicated contracts should exist for:\\n- `scene_director_io_adapter`\\n- `scene_director_output_validator`\\n- `screenplay_merger`\\n- `tts_polish_io_adapter`\\n- `tts_polish_merger`\\n- `retry_planner`\\n- `operator_batch_scheduler`\\n\",\"newText\":\"## Contract coverage guidance\\nDedicated contracts should exist for:\\n- `scene_director_io_adapter`\\n- `scene_director_output_validator`\\n- `screenplay_merger`\\n- `tts_polish_io_adapter`\\n- `tts_polish_merger`\\n- `retry_planner`\\n- `operator_batch_scheduler`\\n\\nDedicated shared deterministic contracts should exist for:\\n- `screenplay_validator`\\n- `polish_validator`\\n- `scene_bible_builder`\\n- `scene_bible_schema_validator`\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gp