t-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\macmini_workspace\\workspace\\skills\\self-improving-agent\\SKILL.md:41:git clone https://github.com/peterskoett/self-improving-agent.git ~/.openclaw/skills/self-improving-agent\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\macmini_workspace\\workspace\\skills\\self-improving-agent\\SKILL.md:91:- **sessions_send** - Send a learning to another session\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\macmini_workspace\\workspace\\skills\\self-improving-agent\\SKILL.md:92:- **sessions_spawn** - Spawn a sub-agent for background work\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\macmini_workspace\\workspace\\skills\\self-improving-agent\\hooks\\openclaw\\HOOK.md:4:metadata: {\"openclaw\":{\"emoji\":\"??\",\"events\":[\"agent:bootstrap\"]}}\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\macmini_workspace\\workspace\\skills\\self-improving-agent\\references\\openclaw-integration.md:68:mkdir -p ~/.openclaw/skills/self-improving-agent/.learnings\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\macmini_workspace\\workspace\\skills\\self-improving-agent\\references\\openclaw-integration.md:83:- Use sessions_send for cross-session communication\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\macmini_workspace\\workspace\\skills\\self-improving-agent\\references\\openclaw-integration.md:175:### sessions_send\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\macmini_workspace\\workspace\\skills\\self-improving-agent\\references\\openclaw-integration.md:179:sessions_send(sessionKey=\"session-id\", message=\"Learning: API requires X-Custom-Header\")\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\macmini_workspace\\workspace\\skills\\self-improving-agent\\references\\openclaw-integration.md:182:### sessions