pus voice message (`opus_48000_64` from ElevenLabs, `opus` from OpenAI).\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tools\\tts.md:328:- **Other channels**: MP3 (`mp3_44100_128` from ElevenLabs, `mp3` from OpenAI).\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tools\\tts.md:333:- Telegram `sendVoice` accepts OGG/MP3/M4A; use OpenAI/ElevenLabs if you need\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tools\\tts.md:337:OpenAI/ElevenLabs output formats are fixed per channel (see above).\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tools\\tts.md:381:/tts provider openai\r\n"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774986277823}}
