rs\\User-OEM\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\reference\\memory-config.md:341:- OpenAI offers discounted pricing for Batch API workloads, so large indexing runs are usually cheaper than sending the same requests synchronously.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\reference\\memory-config.md:342:- See the OpenAI Batch API docs and pricing for details:\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\reference\\memory-config.md:343:- [https://platform.openai.com/docs/api-reference/batch](https://platform.openai.com/docs/api-reference/batch)\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\reference\\memory-config.md:344:- [https://platform.openai.com/pricing](https://platform.openai.com/pricing)\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\reference\\memory-config.md:352:provider: \"openai\",\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\reference\\memory-config.md:354:fallback: \"openai\",\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\reference\\memory-config.md:692:- Fallback: if local setup fails and `memorySearch.fallback = \"openai\"`, we automatically switch to remote embeddings (`openai/text-embedding-3-small` unless overridden) and record the reason.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\reference\\memory-config.md:694:## Custom OpenAI-compatible endpoint example\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\reference\\memory-config.md:700:provider: \"openai\",\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\reference\\memory-config.md:717:- `remote.*` takes precedence over `models.providers.openai.*`.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\reference\\memory-config.md:718:- `remote.headers` merge with OpenAI headers; r