{"type":"message","id":"906efb27","parentId":"bbeadf90","timestamp":"2026-03-31T20:13:39.522Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Vou corrigir o payload de teste para um caso válido, validar o `scene_director` com sucesso real e depois plugar esse protocolo no runtime.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0f234d88709aef6d0169cc2ae4fcd88193a62525fe8aeae6e6\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_MO731PRT7W8chUssSM9kkIP9|fc_0f234d88709aef6d0169cc2af39dfc819399c39358588da320","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\tmp_scene_director_payload.json","content":"{\n  \"job_id\": \"test_job_001\",\n  \"account\": \"004\",\n  \"language\": \"fr\",\n  \"run_root\": \"C:/tmp/test_run\",\n  \"batch\": {\n    \"batch_id\": \"sd_001\",\n    \"start_word\": 1,\n    \"end_word\": 13,\n    \"word_count\": 13,\n    \"text\": \"Les premiers avertissements sont arrivés bien avant que quiconque comprenne ce qu'ils signifiaient.\"\n  },\n  \"scene_words_range\": [8, 20],\n  \"style_context\": {\n    \"channel_name\": \"C004 FRA\",\n    \"reason\": \"integration_test\"\n  },\n  \"instructions\": {\n    \"task\": \"Transform this script batch into an editorially intentional sequence of scenes for screenplay generation.\",\n    \"requirements\": [\n      \"Preserve narrative meaning and order.\",\n      \"Return scene objects only for this batch.\",\n      \"Each scene must include scene_local_id, scene_title, scene_summary, narrative_function, narration_original, start_word, end_word, estimated_scene_word_count.\",\n      \"Use batch-relative word coordinates: the first word in this batch is word 1.\",\n      \"scene_local_id must be sequential within the batch (scene_01, scene_02, ...).\",\n      \"Do not generate global scene IDs.\",\n      \"Do not rewrite the story beyond what is needed for clean scene segmentation.\",\n      \"Do not do visual planning, asset planning, prompt writing, or shot de