{"type":"message","id":"1cdd1450","parentId":"c9a44d7b","timestamp":"2026-03-31T20:15:58.079Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Vou lançar alguns subagentes com Haiku para pesquisar melhores práticas de isolamento/worker execution no OpenClaw e sinais de uso real pela comunidade.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0f234d88709aef6d0169cc2b747578819399a4823f9e71478b\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_IqP9cnd80qufZ6b8i81EVqKR|fc_0f234d88709aef6d0169cc2b7e182c8193a9203636b28e8c3a","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"Research task: Determine best practices for using `openclaw agent` as a deterministic worker/operator execution surface. Focus on isolation, session reuse vs fresh turns, file-based workflows, and whether there are recommended flags/patterns to avoid stale session context. Use official local docs first, then repo evidence, then web/community if needed. Return concrete recommendations and uncertainty clearly marked.","label":"openclaw-worker-best-practices-1","model":"anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5","thinking":"low","cwd":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace","runTimeoutSeconds":600,"timeoutSeconds":30,"thread":false,"mode":"run","cleanup":"keep","sandbox":"inherit"},"partialJson":"{\"task\":\"Research task: Determine best practices for using `openclaw agent` as a deterministic worker/operator execution surface. Focus on isolation, session reuse vs fresh turns, file-based workflows, and whether there are recommended flags/patterns to avoid stale session context. Use official local docs first, then repo evidence, then web/community if needed. Return concrete recommendations and uncertainty clearly marked.\",\"label\":\"openclaw-worker-best-practices-1\",\"model\":\"anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5\",\"thinking\":\"low\",\"cwd\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\",\"runTimeoutSeconds\":600,\"timeoutSeconds\":30,\"thread\":false,\"mode\":\"run\",\"cleanup\":\"keep\",\"sandbox\":\